column5: I have a Lac Seul SE Explorer Series waterproof map, does anyone know where you can buy these maps online? I have searched but can't find the maps I am looking for or the links are not valid. I am most interested in a Minnitaki mapTHANKS!
Someone linked this site before and I bookmarked it.Don't know much else about it.http://www.redlakedigital.com/html/custom_maps.html
I bought mine a couple of months ago from Thorne Brothers for Lac Seul.http://www.thornebros.com/shop/pc/Ca...eries-c333.htm

I have two copies of Minnitaki and if you email your address I will send you one of my copies free. Note that Minnitaki maps are heavy paper, not laminated. If interested send your address to: [email protected]

Not sure if they are still in business or not as I can't find their website anymore, but when I needed a map of Lac Seul last fall someone gave me info for this company and I got one from them. If I remember right, they had numerous lakes available. And you could get them in the nice weatherproof style as well.Alex Wilson Coldstream LtdPhone :(807) 223-2381 Fax (807) 223-2907 Address : PO Box 3009, 32 Colonization Ave, Dryden, ON P8N2Y9
